CustomField.description: This field will have most recent active post acquisition rehab record Id. Here active means Stage in not equals to "Closed - Cancelled". Only time it could have in active is when old active record stage changed to "Closed- Cancelled" and there is no active post acquisition rehab record available.
CustomField.label: Most Recent Post Acq. Rehab
CustomField.relationshipLabel: Residences (Most Recent Active Post Acq. Rehab)
